The paper deals with the detection of botnet campaigns on Twitter, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms and data mining techniques to analyze social media data, which can be categorized under social and information retrieval (cs.SI, cs.IR). Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of botnet campaigns on social media users and society, which can be classified under social networks and society (cs.SOC) and software development (cs.SD).
